@Buddy_budster wrote:

ya first thing u gotta do is make sure they have (characters) folder, second make sure they have (moreinfo) folder they may not always have those.

  1. make sure everything is in one foder in my documents ect…

  2. the normally come with a compiler double click on that

  3. follo its directions.

  4. when thats done you go back to that folder and you should see a runserver file or voule file click on one of thos

  5. your server will be up…

(this is only a brief description)

for a more accurate description go to the server tutorial section… they give very accurate and helpfull desriptions there.

Buddy,
